Symbol.Script_3D:
GROUP "nastil" MATERIAL mat_pl t_nast=0.005 sj=1+2+4+8+16+32 addx bshv addz hshv+t_nast PUT 0,0,sj PUT -A,0,sj PUT -A,-B,sj PUT 0,-B,sj PRISM_ NSP/3, -t_nast, get(NSP) ENDGROUP
GROUP "krep_ogr" MATERIAL mat_ost sj=1+2+4+8+16+32 addx tst addy hshv-a_krep_ogr-tpol PUT 0,0,sj PUT b_krep_ogr,0,sj PUT b_krep_ogr,a_krep_ogr,sj PUT 0,a_krep_ogr,sj hotspot bshv,a_krep_ogr,0 PRISM_ NSP/3, t_krep_ogr, get(NSP) ENDGROUP
GROUP "sred_pol" MATERIAL mat_ost sj=1+2+4+8+16+32 !addx tst addy hshv-a_krep_ogr PUT 0,0,sj PUT -sh_svet,0,sj PUT -sh_svet,a_krep_ogr,sj PUT 0,a_krep_ogr,sj PRISM_ NSP/3, t_krep_ogr, get(NSP) ENDGROUP
del top GROUP "mass_sred_pol" MATERIAL mat_ost rotx 90 addz l1 for i=1 to n PLACEGROUP "sred_pol" addz l2 next i ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP "mass_sred_pol"
del top GROUP "mass_krep_ogr" MATERIAL mat_ost rotx 90 addz 0.3 for i=1 to n1 PLACEGROUP "krep_ogr" addz l3 next i ENDGROUP
GROUP "shveller" MATERIAL mat_ost rotx 90 sj=1+2+4+8+16+32 PUT 0,0,sj if htspt then hotspot 0,0,0 if htspt then hotspot 0,0,lshvel PUT 0,hshv,sj if htspt then hotspot 0,hshv,0 if htspt then hotspot 0,hshv,lshvel PUT bshv,hshv,sj if htspt then hotspot bshv,hshv,0 if htspt then hotspot bshv,hshv,lshvel PUT bshv,hshv-tpol,sj if htspt then hotspot bshv,hshv-tpol,0 if htspt then hotspot bshv,hshv-tpol,lshvel PUT tst,hshv-tpol,sj if htspt then hotspot tst,hshv-tpol,0 if htspt then hotspot tst,hshv-tpol,lshvel PUT tst,tpol,sj if htspt then hotspot tst,tpol,0 if htspt then hotspot tst,tpol,lshvel PUT bshv,tpol,sj if htspt then hotspot bshv,tpol,0 if htspt then hotspot bshv,tpol,lshvel PUT bshv,0,sj if htspt then hotspot bshv,0,0 if htspt then hotspot bshv,0,lshvel PRISM_ NSP/3, B, get(NSP) ENDGROUP
GROUP "ogr" MATERIAL mat_ost muly -1 addx bshv+0.05 addz hshv-b_krep_ogr if ogr then call "Мет. ограждение по серии", parameters l1_krep_ogr=0.3,l2_krep_ogr=l3,n_krep_ogr=n1,l_s=B,l_v=B+2*0.06, h_ogr=h_ogr,b_krep_ogr=b_krep_ogr del top ENDGROUP
GROUP "verh_ugol" MATERIAL mat_ost rotx 90 roty 90 addx -b_ug addy hshv-b_ug sj=1+2+4+8+16+32 h_ug=b_ug PUT 0,0,sj PUT 0,h_ug,sj PUT b_ug,h_ug,sj PUT b_ug,h_ug-t_ug,sj PUT t_ug,h_ug-t_ug,sj PUT t_ug,0,sj PRISM_ NSP/3, -sh_svet, get(NSP) ENDGROUP
MATERIAL mat_pl PLACEGROUP "nastil" MATERIAL mat_ost PLACEGROUP "verh_ugol" addy -B muly -1 PLACEGROUP "verh_ugol" del top PLACEGROUP "shveller" if krogr then PLACEGROUP "mass_krep_ogr" PLACEGROUP "ogr" del top mulx -1 addx sh_svet PLACEGROUP "shveller" if krogr then PLACEGROUP "mass_krep_ogr" PLACEGROUP "ogr"

Symbol.Script_PR:
dlin_prof = B spokr = SURFACE3D() ves = VOLUME3D()*7850 ves = ves + ves*proc_zap pos = GLOB_ID
if type_spec = "Металл" then gosub "spec_m" endif if type_spec = "Изделие" then gosub "spec_i" endif
if uch_pokr then tip_el = "30" komment = "кв.м." obozn = "см. примечания" naen = "Покрытие " + mat_pokr kol_vo_spec = spokr call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, obozn=obozn, naen=naen, kol_vo_spec=spokr, komment=komment endif
goto 20 "spec_m": tip_el = "20" for i = 1 to kol_vo_spec call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, pos = pos, tip_konstr=tip_konstr, stal_gost=stal_gost, mater=mater, obozn=obozn, tip_profile=tip_profile, dlin_prof=dlin_prof, ves=round_int(ves/dlin_prof), naen=naen, otm_elem=SYMB_POS_Z next i return
"spec_i": tip_el = "40" call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, pos = pos, obozn=obozn, naen=naen, ves=ves, kol_vo_spec=1, komment="", otm_elem=SYMB_POS_Z return 20:
Symbol.Script_VL:
CALL "Общий шаблон сталь" parameters all PARAMETERS ZZYZX = hshv values "A" 0.704,0.904,CUSTOM values "B" 0.9,1.2,1.5,1.8,2.1,2.4,3,3.6,4.2,4.8,5.4,6,CUSTOM values "h_ogr" 1,1.2 !if B<3 then !PARAMETERS hshv=0.12 !PARAMETERS bshv=0.052 !PARAMETERS tpol=0.0078 !PARAMETERS tst=0.0048 !else !PARAMETERS hshv=0.14 !PARAMETERS bshv=0.058 !PARAMETERS tpol=0.0081 !PARAMETERS tst=0.0049 !endif
PARAMETERS sh_svet = A - 2 * bshv index_l1 = 2 : index_l2 = 3 : index_l3 = 4 : index_n = 5 : index_n1 = 6 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="B" then for i=1 to 12 if inf[i][1]=B then PARAMETERS l1=inf[i][index_l1] PARAMETERS l2=inf[i][index_l2] PARAMETERS l3=inf[i][index_l3] PARAMETERS n=inf[i][index_n]*1000+1 PARAMETERS n1=inf[i][index_n1]*1000+1 if n = 1 and l2 > 0 then PARAMETERS n = 2 PARAMETERS l2 = B - 2 * l1 endif if n1 = 1 and l3 = 0 then PARAMETERS n1 = 2 PARAMETERS l3 = B - 2 * 0.3 endif endif next i endif
PARAMETERS obozn = "Серия 1.450.3-7.94" naen = "Площадка ПГФ" PARAMETERS tip_profile = naen naen = naen+"-" naen = naen+str("%.0mm",B/100)+"."+str("%.0mm",A/100) PARAMETERS naen = naen
